snippet.title: Bits & Bops Gameplay Demo
snippet.description:
Wishlist Bits & Bops on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1929290/Bits__Bops/

Future Bits & Bops videos will be posted to the Tempo Lab Games channel:
https://www.youtube.com/@TempoLabGames

Join the Bits & Bops community Discord for news and events:
https://discord.gg/vXFYSbmbXz

Follow us on Twitter for Bits & Bops updates:
https://twitter.com/TempoLabGames

Gameplay demo for upcoming rhythm game Bits & Bops by Tempo Lab Games.
